截自2020年1月28日，[[美国|美国]]的人口總數估計約有329,227,746人<ref name="clock">{{cite web|title=Population Clock|url=https://www.census.gov/popclock/|publisher=United States Census Bureau|access-date=2020-10-11|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117025617/http://www.census.gov/popclock/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国人口高度城镇化，在2008年时约有81%人口居住在城市及其郊区（同时期世界城镇化率为54%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2212.html |title=CIA World Factbook |accessdate=2010-12-11 |publisher=[[CIA_World_Factbook|CIA World Factbook]] |date=December 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514223816/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2212.html |archivedate=2011-05-14 }}</ref>），这使得美国有许多土地上无人居住<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/us.html |title=CIA World Factbook |accessdate=2010-12-11 |publisher=[[CIA_World_Factbook|CIA World Factbook]] |archive-date=2017-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801085713/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/us.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加利福尼亚州与得克萨斯州是人口最多的两个州份<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.census.gov/compendia/statab/2010/tables/10s0013.xls |title=Table 13. State Population - Rank, Percent Change, and Population Density |accessdate=2010-10-24 |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |year=2008 |format=[[Microsoft_Excel|Excel]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101009232259/http://www.census.gov/compendia/statab/2010/tables/10s0013.xls |archivedate=2010-10-09 }}</ref>，美国人口中心持续向西南倾斜，[[德克薩斯州|德州]]、[[加州|加州]]、[[犹他州|犹他州]]等西南诸州人口增长较快，而历史悠久的东北部各州（[[纽约州|纽约州]]、[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]、[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]）等地则人口停滞甚至下降<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/cenpop/meanctr.pdf |title=Mean Center of Population for the United States: 1790 to 2000 |accessdate=2010-10-24 |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20011103033717/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/cenpop/meanctr.pdf |archivedate=2001-11-03 }}</ref>。纽约市则是美国人口最多的城市<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/popest/cities/SUB-EST2009.html|title=Annual Estimates of the Resident Population for Incorporated Places over 110,000, Ranked by July 1, 2009 Population: April 1, 2000 to July 1, 2009 (SUB-EST2009-01)|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=2011-05-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514000702/http://www.census.gov/popest/cities/SUB-EST2009.html|archivedate=2011年5月14日}}</ref>。

根据2015年的美国[[总和生育率|总和生育率]]，每个女性约拥有1.84个儿童，并每年逐步下降，已经低于人口恒定所需要的“每个女性2个儿童”标准线，[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]数据显示，截止2013年美国的人口增长率为0.72%，不过仍然低于世界年均增长率（1.09%）<ref name=ciapgr/>；然而美国的人口增长率在[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]中名列前茅<ref name=ciapgr>{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2002.html |title=CIA - The World Factbook -- Field Listing - Population growth rate |accessdate=2012-01-09 |publisher=[[Central_Intelligence_Agency|CIA]] |archive-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625150251/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2002.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，这是因为美国每年接纳超过100万移民，对保持人口的数量增长更为重要<ref name=ciafertility>{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2127rank.html |title=CIA - The World Factbook -- Rank Order - Total fertility rate |accessdate=2010-02-01 |publisher=[[Central_Intelligence_Agency|CIA]] |archive-date=2009-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028133713/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2127rank.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2112rank.html |title=CIA - The World Factbook -- Rank Order - Net migration rate |accessdate=2009-02-23 |publisher=[[Central_Intelligence_Agency|CIA]] |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226005157/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2112rank.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，数据显示，2016年有超過149萬人移民美國，相比2015年的138萬增長7％，數量並逐年增加<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.migrationpolicy.org/article/frequently-requested-statistics-immigrants-and-immigration-united-states |title=Frequently Requested Statistics on Immigrants and Immigration in the United States |accessdate=2018-02-08 |archive-date=2021-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209224529/https://www.migrationpolicy.org/article/frequently-requested-statistics-immigrants-and-immigration-united-states |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自20世纪以来，美国人口增长三倍多。从1900年的7600万增至2015年的3.2亿，每年增长1.3%。目前，[[少数民族|少数民族]]人口增长速度最快。根据人口局对2012年的估算，50.4%小于一岁的美国孩子属于少数民族（包括非洲裔、亚裔、拉美裔、混血、原住民等）<ref>[http://www.washingtonpost.com/local/census-minority-babies-are-now-majority-in-united-states/2012/05/16/gIQA1WY8UU_story.html Morello, Carol and Mellnik, Ted. "Census: Minority Babies Are Now Majority in United States." ''Washington Post.'' May 17, 2012.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/local/census-minority-babies-are-now-majority-in-united-states/2012/05/16/gIQA1WY8UU_story.html |date=20210320175330 }} Accessed 2012-05-17.</ref>。 据[[美国普查局|美国人口普查局]]2020人口普查的结果显示，白人在美国人口中的占比自有记录以来首次降至低于60%，而多元种族或有色人种的人口如今超过了40%。 过去十年，美国人口增长了7.4%，为上世纪30年代以来的最低水平。<ref>{{Cite web|title=美国2020年人口普查：白人占比首次跌破60%|url=http://www.ftchinese.com/premium/001093554?full=y#ccode=iosaction|access-date=2021-08-13|work=FT中文网|archive-date=2022-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220115001831/http://www.ftchinese.com/premium/001093554?full=y#ccode=iosaction|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=美国白人人口首次下降，亚裔和西语裔人口激增|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20210813/census-demographics-asian-hispanic/|access-date=2021-08-13|date=2021-08-13|last=Tavernise|first=Sabrina|work=纽约时报中文网|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2022-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220225191041/https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20210813/census-demographics-asian-hispanic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

